		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sorry for bumping this again!<br /><br />0.3.1 is out:<br /><br />-VRC7 sound support<br />-MMC5 vertical split mode support<br />-Input devices (i.e controller, zapper, four player adapter) are now automatically selected when loading a recognized rom<br />-Improved support for VS System (automatically selects the proper PPU palette and input mappings)<br />-Plus a few bug fixes and small improvements

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


