		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A couple of updates - 0.3.2 and 0.4.0 have been released.<br /><br />Updates:<br />-Added support for 46 more mappers<br />-DirectInput devices are now supported<br />-UI is now also available in Spanish &amp; Russian<br />-Controller button state can now be shown on the screen<br />-Fixed a DirectX crash that caused the emu to crash on some computers<br />-Fixed an audio bug with the square channel sweep unit<br />-Improved open bus implementation (passes &quot;allpads&quot; test)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


