		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm in portable mode now. I don't see where Mesen is storing it's cheat files such as Game Genie and Pro Action Replay. Do does anyone know where those are saved to and what formats Mesen accepts. I have a few cheats packs I would like to import if possible.

		

		</td>
